{
  "title": "Polymarket — Scanner & Whale Analytics",
  "uid": "polymarket-overview",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": { "from": "now-7d", "to": "now" },
  "description": "Polymarket service observability: market scanner, opportunities, simulated positions, and on-chain whale analytics (Phase A). Extended in Phase B with reject reasons, Kelly sizing, and exit triggers.",
  "panels": [

    { "type": "row", "id": 100, "title": "Scanner Summary", "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 1 }, "collapsed": false },

    {
      "id": 101, "type": "stat", "title": "Markets scanned (1h)",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 1, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "blue" } } },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "increase(polymarket_markets_scanned_total[1h])",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" } }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" }
    },
    {
      "id": 102, "type": "stat", "title": "Opportunities (24h)",
      "gridPos": { "x": 6, "y": 1, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
        "thresholds": { "steps": [
          { "color": "blue", "value": null },
          { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
        ] } } },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "increase(polymarket_opportunities_total[24h])",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" } }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" }
    },
    {
      "id": 103, "type": "stat", "title": "Open simulated positions",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 1, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "purple" } } },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "polymarket_positions_open",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" } }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" }
    },
    {
      "id": 104, "type": "stat", "title": "Opportunity rate (per 100 scans)",
      "description": "Rough yield of the scanner — very high values warrant checking for prompt/config drift.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 18, "y": 1, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "none",
        "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
        "thresholds": { "steps": [
          { "color": "green", "value": null },
          { "color": "yellow", "value": 10 },
          { "color": "red", "value": 25 }
        ] } } },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "100 * increase(polymarket_opportunities_total[24h]) / clamp_min(increase(polymarket_markets_scanned_total[24h]), 1)",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
      }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" }
    },

    { "type": "row", "id": 200, "title": "Whale Analytics (Phase A)", "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 5, "w": 24, "h": 1 }, "collapsed": false },

    {
      "id": 201, "type": "stat", "title": "Whales tracked",
      "description": "Count of wallets meeting min_trades AND min_win_rate AND min_pnl thresholds from strategy_config.yaml.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 6, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
        "thresholds": { "steps": [
          { "color": "red", "value": null },
          { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
          { "color": "green", "value": 10 }
        ] } } },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "polymarket_whales_tracked",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" } }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" }
    },
    {
      "id": 202, "type": "stat", "title": "Events consumed (last refresh)",
      "gridPos": { "x": 6, "y": 6, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "blue" } } },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "polymarket_whale_events_seen",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" } }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" }
    },
    {
      "id": 203, "type": "stat", "title": "Hours since last refresh",
      "description": "Warn if this exceeds the configured refresh_hours (default 24h).",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 6, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "h",
        "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
        "thresholds": { "steps": [
          { "color": "green", "value": null },
          { "color": "yellow", "value": 26 },
          { "color": "red", "value": 48 }
        ] } } },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "(time() - polymarket_whale_refresh_last_success_timestamp) / 3600",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
      }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" }
    },
    {
      "id": 204, "type": "stat", "title": "Refresh failures (24h)",
      "gridPos": { "x": 18, "y": 6, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
        "thresholds": { "steps": [
          { "color": "green", "value": null },
          { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
          { "color": "red", "value": 3 }
        ] } } },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "increase(polymarket_whale_refresh_failures_total[24h])",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" } }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" }
    },

    {
      "id": 210, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Whale refresh duration",
      "description": "p50/p95 of whale refresh wall-clock time. Watch for growth indicating subgraph slowness or event-volume creep.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 10, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s",
        "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10 } } },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.5, sum by (le) (rate(polymarket_whale_refresh_duration_seconds_bucket[6h])))",
          "legendFormat": "p50",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" } },
        { "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(polymarket_whale_refresh_duration_seconds_bucket[6h])))",
          "legendFormat": "p95",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" } }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 211, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Whales tracked over time",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 10, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10 } } },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "polymarket_whales_tracked",
        "legendFormat": "whales",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" } }]
    },

    { "type": "row", "id": 300, "title": "Scanner Rejections (Phase B)", "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 18, "w": 24, "h": 1 }, "collapsed": false },

    {
      "id": 301, "type": "piechart", "title": "Reject reasons (24h)",
      "description": "Why candidate markets were rejected before reaching Claude. Heavy 'depth' or 'volume' skew means tunables in strategy_config.yaml may be too strict.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 19, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" } } },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "values": ["value", "percent"] }, "pieType": "donut" },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "sum by (reason) (increase(polymarket_rejects_total[24h]))",
        "legendFormat": "{{reason}}",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
      }]
    },
    {
      "id": 302, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Reject rate over time",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 19, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10, "stacking": { "mode": "normal" } } } },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "sum by (reason) (rate(polymarket_rejects_total[1h]))",
        "legendFormat": "{{reason}}",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
      }]
    },

    { "type": "row", "id": 400, "title": "Sizing & Whale Concurrence (Phase B)", "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 27, "w": 24, "h": 1 }, "collapsed": false },

    {
      "id": 401, "type": "bargauge", "title": "Kelly fraction distribution",
      "description": "Histogram of f* values at opportunity-creation time. Quarter-Kelly cap is 0.25 — any bucket at 0.25 represents capped positions.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 28, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "none", "color": { "mode": "continuous-GrYlRd" } } },
      "options": { "displayMode": "gradient", "orientation": "horizontal" },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "sum by (le) (increase(polymarket_kelly_fraction_bucket[7d]))",
        "format": "heatmap",
        "legendFormat": "{{le}}",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
      }]
    },
    {
      "id": 402, "type": "stat", "title": "Whale concurrences (7d)",
      "description": "Opportunities where at least one tracked whale holds the same side. Currently a feature flag, not an auto-trade trigger.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 28, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green" } } },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "increase(polymarket_whale_concurrences_total[7d])",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" } }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" }
    },
    {
      "id": 403, "type": "stat", "title": "Whale concurrence rate",
      "description": "Share of opportunities over the last 7d that had whale agreement.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 18, "y": 28, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "percentunit",
        "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
        "thresholds": { "steps": [
          { "color": "blue", "value": null },
          { "color": "green", "value": 0.1 }
        ] } } },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "increase(polymarket_whale_concurrences_total[7d]) / clamp_min(increase(polymarket_opportunities_total[7d]), 1)",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
      }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" }
    },

    { "type": "row", "id": 500, "title": "Exit Monitor (Phase B)", "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 36, "w": 24, "h": 1 }, "collapsed": false },

    {
      "id": 501, "type": "piechart", "title": "Exit reasons (30d)",
      "description": "How simulated positions closed. Heavy 'stale_thesis' means Claude's probability estimates are not moving the market — a Phase C calibration signal.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 37, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" } } },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "values": ["value", "percent"] }, "pieType": "donut" },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "sum by (reason) (increase(polymarket_exits_total[30d]))",
        "legendFormat": "{{reason}}",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
      }]
    },
    {
      "id": 502, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Exits by reason over time",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 37, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10 } } },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "sum by (reason) (increase(polymarket_exits_total[1d]))",
        "legendFormat": "{{reason}}",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
      }]
    },

    { "type": "row", "id": 900, "title": "Whale roster & open positions (data inspection)", "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 45, "w": 24, "h": 1 }, "collapsed": false },
    {
      "id": 901, "type": "text", "title": "How to view the current whale roster",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 46, "w": 12, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "The ranked roster of profitable wallets is stored in Redis and SQLite, not Prometheus (addresses + PnL values don't fit the metric model). To inspect the current set:\n\n```bash\ndocker compose exec redis redis-cli GET signals:polymarket:whales:summary | jq '.top[0:20]'\ndocker compose exec polymarket sqlite3 /app/data/polymarket.db \\\n    'SELECT address, trades, win_rate, total_pnl FROM whales ORDER BY total_pnl DESC LIMIT 20'\n```\n\nThe set refreshes every 24h (configurable via `prediction_markets.whales.refresh_hours`)."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 902, "type": "text", "title": "How to view open simulated positions",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 46, "w": 12, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Positions carry Phase B metadata (expected_gap, kelly_fraction, whale_concurrence, claude_model) that Phase C's calibration harness consumes. Inspect with:\n\n```bash\ndocker compose exec polymarket sqlite3 /app/data/polymarket.db \\\n    'SELECT id, market_id, side, entry_price, amount_usd, kelly_fraction, whale_concurrence, opened_at \\\n     FROM positions WHERE closed_at IS NULL AND simulation=1 ORDER BY opened_at DESC'\n```\n\nAll rows are `simulation=1` — enforced as a literal in `publish_opportunity()` (see `tests/test_no_live_orders.py`)."
      }
    }
  ],
  "templating": {
    "list": [{
      "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS", "type": "datasource", "pluginId": "prometheus",
      "hide": 2, "current": { "text": "Prometheus", "value": "prometheus" }
    }]
  }
}
